name: Emilia Clarke [Embedding]
description:
The very first embedding I created with some moderate success. I'm aware there's an entire checkpoint model out there for recreating her likeness and compared to that, an embedding is somewhat limited. Still, I have managed to create good images using this embedding and I hope you can do so as well.

As usual, this embedding has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. I've run into issues using the embedding with certain models such as RealisticVision 1.3. Lowering the embedding weight or using inpainting to re-generate the face really helps here.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
